name: PASCA LISAN X (MESIN + CAHAYA BINTANG BUATAN) Trailer 2
description:
Sito Fossy Biosa, 2021

The process to success and the relation of our struggles and dreams is shared in this art house short video. The youth movement in Indonesia was critically damaged by terrorist acts until Covid-19, resulting in their freedom to be slowly diminished. Every sweat, tear, and blood has hope. Time is precious to us, but in every journey there will always be parties who carries the potential to harm our journey and the future of our generations. Time is a testament of proof towards who is strong enough to go through it all and we can only hope to keep on moving like machines, as everything has been designed by power.

Please visit www.pinktank.art for more information.
